  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In a randomized, sham-controlled trial the investigators will test whether supplemental
      oxygen given during cardiopulmonary exercise testing will improve exercise performance and
      physiological parameters in patients with pulmonary arterial or chronic thromboembolic
      pulmonary hypertension.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
